title: 7: No Such Thing As The Loch Ness Monster
content: This week in the QI Office Dan Schreiber (@schreiberland), James Harkin (@jamesharkin), Anna Ptaszynski (@nosuchthing) and Andrew Hunter Murray (@andrewhunterm) discuss parachuting dogs, a misbehaving coconut, the longest game in the world & more...
